        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "[codex] support command cron jobs",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds a first-class command payload for cron jobs so scheduled shell-style work can run directly through the gateway scheduler instead of being forced through an isolated agent/model run.\n\nThis wires command cron payloads through the protocol schema, cron persistence/normalization, CLI add/edit flows, gateway execution, delivery suppression, and UI preservation for existing command jobs. The UI can display and preserve command jobs, but command authoring remains CLI-first in this PR.\n\n## Behavior addressed\n\nBehavior addressed: Scheduled command jobs can be stored and executed as command payloads by the gateway cron runner, including stdout/stderr capture, timeout handling, output limits, and `NO_REPLY` suppression.\n\nReal environment tested: Local OpenClaw source checkout on macOS; no deployed gateway was modified.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/gateway/server-cron.test.ts src/cron/store.test.ts src/cron/normalize.test.ts src/cron/command-runner.test.ts src/cli/cron-cli.test.ts src/agents/tools/cron-tool.test.ts packages/gateway-protocol/src/cron-validators.test.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/cron.test.ts`; `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`; `AUTOREVIEW_AUTO_TESTS=0 .agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --prompt 'Only report P0/P1 correctness, data-loss, security, or production-breakage findings. Omit P2/P3 findings entirely.'`; `pnpm build`.\n\nEvidence after fix: Focused Vitest shards passed: unit 16 tests, gateway 23 tests, cron 89 tests, CLI 87 tests, agents 100 tests, UI 40 tests. `git diff --check` passed. P0/P1-scoped autoreview reported no accepted/actionable findings. `pnpm build` completed successfully.\n\nObserved result after fix: Command cron payloads validate, persist, normalize, execute, report output, suppress silent output, and round-trip through the tested CLI/store/UI surfaces.\n\nWhat was not tested: A live deployed gateway cron run was not executed; CI has not run yet.\n",
